      <div style=3D"font-family:Montserrat, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-=
height:1.2;text-align:left;color:rgb(255,255,255);"><p><span style=3D"color=
:#02ea95"><strong>FOOD &amp; FACILITIES</strong></span><br/>
Throughout the day, food and drinks will be provided. We=E2=80=99ve taken p=
articipants=E2=80=99 preferences into account as much as possible and kindl=
y ask you to help us avoid unnecessary waste.</p>
<p><br/>
<span style=3D"color:#02ea95"><strong>MEET THE JURY OF BRABANTHACK_26</stro=
ng></span><br/>
We are proud to present our Jury:</p>
<p><a href=3D"https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephanie-ottenheijm-902503/">Ste=
phanie Ottenheijm</a><br/>
Lead AI/Data - Digital Holland<br/>
=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B<br/>
