CEO -=C2=A0Brabant Development Agency (BOM) - Chair of the Jury</p>
<p><br/>
<strong><span style=3D"color:#02ea95">BUILDING WITH AWS - FINAL REMINDER</s=
pan></strong><br/>
<em>Following up on our earlier message shared on behalf of Amazon Web Serv=
ices (AWS):</em></p>
<p>During BrabantHack_26, participants can make use of <strong>temporary AW=
S accounts</strong>, including a range of AI services and development tools=
 such as Amazon Bedrock, Kiro CLI, Lambda, DynamoDB, S3 and more. This can =
significantly support teams who want to experiment with building AI-powered=
 solutions in the cloud.</p>
<p>To help you prepare, AWS is hosting a 1=E2=80=91hour <strong>=E2=80=9CGe=
tting Started=E2=80=9D online session:</strong></p>
<p>Date: <strong>Thursday, April 9</strong><br/>
Time: <strong>9:00 AM</strong><br/>
Join via Microsoft Teams:<br/>
<span style=3D"color:#02ea95">https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/360232308675=
069?p=3DOwYGzkzUKiRIv86rSx</span></p>
<p>If you have questions related to this offer, you can reach out to Hasan =
Akirmak (<a href=3D"mailto:akirmak@amazon.nl"><span style=3D"color:#02ea95"=
>akirmak@amazon.nl</span></a>). Startup founders with broader AWS inquiries=
 can contact Sebastiaan Mook (<a href=3D"mailto:sebamook@amazon.nl"><span s=
tyle=3D"color:#02ea95">sebamook@amazon.nl</span></a>).<br/>
=C2=A0</p>
<p><span style=3D"color:#02ea95"><strong>SNOWFLAKE</strong></span><br/>
We have more great news: <strong>Snowflake</strong> is supporting BrabantHa=
ck_26 by offering access to <strong>Snowflake=E2=80=99s Data Cloud platform=
</strong>. Participants who want to work with Snowflake, please click on=C2=
=A0<a href=3D"https://signup.snowflake.com/?k=3Dhol-snowflake-6049&amp;t=3D=
b6db41dccb99c1ff30d47bae48c726524600996598b8ddec954c0098760e4370"><span sty=
le=3D"color:#02ea95">this link</span></a>=C2=A0if you want to use a trial w=
ith $400 in free credits.=C2=A0</p>
<p>=C2=A0</p>
<p>We=E2=80=99re excited to meet you and can=E2=80=99t wait to kick off Bra=
bantHack_26 together!<br/>
<strong>Less talk. More hack.</strong></p>
<p>Best regards,<br/>
